description: Phase 2 details of design and external appearance comprising fourteen 4-bedroomed detached houses, sixteen 4-bedroomed and six 3-bedroomed semi-detached houses, twenty-six 4-bedroomed and four 3-bedroomed terraced houses, forty 2-bedroomed and six 1-bedroomed self-contained flats in a mixture of two, three and four-storey buildings together with garages, surface and basement car parking (pursuant to App. No. 02/48600/OUT).
